{"type":"text","timestamp":1775881731645,"sessionID":"ses_285348e62ffegeKpO7eZ8W2tjC","part":{"id":"prt_d7accb4b3001tNWEKQvZEEGQCC","messageID":"msg_d7accab1c001YQeV55d5EssM5i","sessionID":"ses_285348e62ffegeKpO7eZ8W2tjC","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis, the design document specifies `cmd/workload-manager`, `cmd/router`, and `cmd/picod` as source paths, but these directories don't exist in the actual codebase. The actual components are in `cmd/agentcube`, `cmd/agentcube-admin`, `cmd/agentd`, etc. However, since the task says to follow the spec strictly and the design document provides explicit paths, I'll create the Dockerfiles that reference the paths as specified in the design (which may need to be created or the paths adjusted based on actual structure).\n\nLet me read the design document more carefully for the exact paths:","time":{"start":1775881731643,"end":1775881731643}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775881733137,"sessionID":"ses_285348e62ffegeKpO7eZ8W2tjC","part":{"id":"prt_d7accbe3e001U5dHOqRzl8tGoK","messageID":"msg_d7accab1c001YQeV55d5EssM5i","sessionID":"ses_285348e62ffegeKpO7eZ8W2tjC","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_9044d214c78d4537aafdab91","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 completed |\n12: \n13: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架提供 Kubernetes-native 的 HTTP API，用于管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 工作负载。该服务封装了 client-go 的复杂性，为 Python SDK、CLI 工具和其他消费者提供简化的 RESTful 接口。\n14: \n15: ## Architecture\n16: \n17: ### 组件分层\n18: \n19: ```\n20: Client (SDK/CLI/Frontend)\n21:   ↓ HTTPS\n22: Gin Router (:8080)\n23:   ↓\n24: Middleware Stack\n25:   ├─ LoggingMiddleware\n26:   ├─ RecoveryMiddleware\n27:   ├─ CORSMiddleware\n28:   └─ AuthMiddleware (optional)\n29:   ↓\n30: HTTP Handlers\n31:   ├─ AgentRuntime Handlers\n32:   ├─ CodeInterpreter Handlers\n33:   ├─ Health Handlers\n34:   └─ Metrics Handler\n35:   ↓\n36: Service Layer (WorkloadManager Interface)\n37:   ↓\n38: Kubernetes Client Layer\n39:   ├─ typed client (AgentRuntimeInterface, CodeInterpreterInterface)\n40:   ├─ informers (SharedInformerFactory)\n41:   └─ listers (AgentRuntimeLister, CodeInterpreterLister)\n42:   ↓\n43: Kubernetes API Server\n44: ```\n45: \n46: ### 目录结构\n47: \n48: ```\n49: pkg/workloadmanager/\n50: ├── server.go              # Gin server setup, router configuration, graceful shutdown\n51: ├── service.go             # WorkloadManager interface definition\n52: ├── client.go              # Kubernetes client initialization\n53: ├── types.go               # API request/response DTOs\n54: ├── handlers/\n55: │   ├── agentruntime.go    # AgentRuntime CRUD handlers\n56: │   ├── codeinterpreter.go # CodeInterpreter CRUD handlers\n57: │   ├── health.go          # Health check handlers (/healthz, /readyz)\n58: │   └── metrics.go         # Prometheus metrics handler\n59: ├── middleware/\n60: │   ├── auth.go            # JWT/Kubernetes TokenReview authentication\n61: │   ├── logging.go         # Request logging\n62: │   └── error.go           # Centralized error handling\n63: └── store/\n64:     └── store.go           # Store interface (Redis-backed)\n65: ```\n66: \n67: ### 启动流程\n68: \n69: ```go\n70: main():\n71:   1. LoadConfig() — 从环境变量和 flags 加载配置\n72:   2. NewK8sClient() — 初始化 Kubernetes clientset\n73:   3. NewSharedInformerFactory() — 创建 informer factory\n74:   4. RegisterInformers() — 注册 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter informers\n75:   5. StartInformers() — 启动 informers 并等待 cache sync\n76:   6. NewWorkloadManager() — 初始化 service layer\n77:   7. NewServer() — 创建 Gin server\n78:   8. RegisterRoutes() — 注册 HTTP routes\n79:   9. StartServer() — 监听端口，阻塞直到 shutdown\n80: ```\n81: \n82: ## Data Structures\n83: \n84: ### API 请求/响应类型\n85: \n86: ```go\n87: // pkg/workloadmanager/types.go\n88: \n89: // APIResponse 标准 API 响应包装器\n90: type APIResponse struct {\n91:     Success bool        `json:\"success\"`\n92:     Data    interface{} `json:\"data,omitempty\"`\n93:     Error   *APIError   `json:\"error,omitempty\"`\n94: }\n95: \n96: // APIError 标准化错误响应\n97: type APIError struct {\n98:     Code    string `json:\"code\"`\n99:     Message string `json:\"message\"`\n100:     Details string `json:\"details,omitempty\"`\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 1135. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 completed |\n\nWorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架提供 Kubernetes-native 的 HTTP API，用于管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 工作负载。该服务封装了 client-go 的复杂性，为 Python SDK、CLI 工具和其他消费者提供简化的 RESTful 接口。\n\n## Architecture\n\n### 组件分层\n\n```\nClient (SDK/CLI/Frontend)","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md","time":{"start":1775881733119,"end":1775881733135}}}}
